node.text:
I used to compete in high school. I went to Orange County and played this piece brilliantly and got cheated out of an opportunity to progress in the competition. They couldn’t understand how a ghetto kid from inglewood with corn rows could master a difficult classical piece. 
But we kept going. 
7
